
  Sleep Sounds: White Noise Mix

  Last updated: April 3, 2026

  Introduction

  This Privacy Policy describes how Sleep Sounds: White Noise Mix ("we", "our", or "the app") handles
  information when you use our mobile application. We are committed to protecting your privacy.

  Information We Collect

  Information We Do NOT Collect

  Our app does not collect, store, or share any personal information such as:
  - Name, email address, or phone number
  - Photos, videos, or files
  - Precise location
  - Contacts or calendar data
  - Health or fitness data
  - Financial or payment information
  - Messages or chat data

  Our app does not require user registration or account creation.

  Information Collected by Third Parties

  Our app displays advertisements provided by Google AdMob. AdMob may automatically collect certain
  information to serve and personalize ads, including:

  - Device identifiers (such as advertising ID)
  - Approximate location (based on IP address)
  - App interaction data (ad views, clicks, and impressions)
  - Diagnostics data (crash logs, performance data)

  This data is collected and processed by Google in accordance with
  https://policies.google.com/privacy.

  How We Use Information

  The app itself stores only local preferences on your device (such as timer settings and volume
  preferences) using local storage. This data never leaves your device and is not accessible to us.

  Third-Party Services

  Our app uses the following third-party services:

  - Google AdMob — for displaying advertisements. AdMob may use cookies and device identifiers to
  serve personalized ads. You can opt out of personalized advertising by adjusting your device
  settings:
    - On Android: Settings > Google > Ads > Opt out of Ads Personalization

  For more information, please refer to:
  - https://policies.google.com/privacy
  - https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites

  Data Retention

  We do not store any user data on external servers. All app preferences are stored locally on your
  device and can be removed by uninstalling the app or clearing the app's data.

  Children's Privacy

  Our app is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal
  information from children under 13. The app's target audience is users aged 13 and above.

  Data Security

  Since we do not collect or transmit personal data, there is minimal risk to your privacy. All app
  data is stored locally on your device.

  Changes to This Privacy Policy

  We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected by updating the
  "Last updated" date at the top of this policy. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy
  periodically.

